text: Minidoka County is a county in the U.S. state of Idaho. As of the 2020 census, 21,613 people lived there. The county seat and largest city is Rupert. == Communities == === Cities === * Acequia * Burley (part) * Heyburn * Minidoka * Paul * Rupert == References == Category:1913 establishments in Idaho Category:Idaho counties
